    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving 4.0L S65 V8 engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the M-specific subframe and aluminum suspension components. Power is managed through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes an inspection of the rod bearings and throttle actuators. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity remains high, providing a pure, analog driving experience.",
